snippet.title: Courier 79 Early Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Hello, I'm back with yet another game. Now we are talking about a delivery rogue-like. 

Courier 79 Early Demo is now available for free here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2558350/Courier_79/

and here: 
https://corrox.itch.io/courier-79-demo

Also if you'd like to participate in shaping this or my future games, join my discord server: https://discord.gg/EYSm7cSmXJ
